i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13ce3566a144e2cea0f72b3368ff73ac15c5921","tid":2204663,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"咁都叫縱火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火頭又唔係佢起"},{"pid":"033e7bf9b48838b0393da6eab0fa8929d202a429","tid":2204663,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"「青少年罪犯報告」係咩撚嘢人寫㗎<br />\n似想鳩UP老屈"},{"pid":"5343011397ce61b4e5c4d7b63fd71f4d1cdfa0e3","tid":2204663,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033e7bf9b48838b0393da6eab0fa8929d202a429","tid":2204663,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"「青少年罪犯報告」係咩撚嘢人寫㗎<br />\n似想鳩UP老屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"青少年罪犯評估專案小組是由懲教署及社會福利署的專業人員所組成，專責就年齡介乎十四至不足二十五歲的男性罪犯及十四至不足二十一歲的女性罪犯的個案，向裁判官/法官提供關於判刑的綜合專業意見。<br />\n<br />\n專案小組成員會研究法庭轉介的個案，並在其後遞交法庭的報告中，推薦最適合的自新計劃供法庭參考，以協助對定罪的青少年罪犯作出判刑。此外，當監管機構認為個別正在實行自新計劃的青少年罪犯有需要轉換另一更合適的計劃時，專案小組亦可再就轉介而作出研究，並提供進一步的建議。"},{"pid":"f86ab89a704e29c13b6f27f0b5868bf83514487f","tid":2204663,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dece519fbc3020683fda3acd588923bd5c44058","tid":2204663,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ffbe62f3ea541969b0626cebd5b6eed4bfa7545","tid":2204663,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:34:33.000Z","msg":"到最尾都要追700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"控方真係去到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:41:39.0